node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'hiph How I Made $1.2 Million Dollars Profit Selling Online Without Creating Products (Storytime) @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'bjh On April 28th, 2015, 5:03 PM my restaurant burned to the ground, I was late on insurance payments and so I got no compensation and lost everything @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'bjh I was washing dishes at Hilton hotels to pay my employees their due salaries while washing cars on the side just to survive. @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'hih In 2015 I saw a 20-something in a tank top flex a Lambo and a Rolex on Youtube claiming he made it on Amazon. I ignored him for being a poser @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'hjh But the idea didn't let me go idea and so I researched Amazon FBA on Youtube and Google until| felt confident ordering products and selling them online @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, sky and text that says 'hjh I failed horribly because the free knowledge wasn't preparing me for the challenges ahead and I lost $7,000 ($5k of which belonged to my girlfriend's mother) @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'hjh After 3 failed attempts I swallowed my pride and bought a course about FBA. It was a crappy 8hrs course but binged it and it gave me what I needed. @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'bjh Shortly after, launched my first successful products, replicated the process, and did it again and again... @basharjkatou'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'hjh 2017 made 60k in profits, 2018 $250k, 2019 I hit $1.2 million and just last year I hit complete financial freedom and retired my parents. @basharjkatou'.

Photo shared by Business Blurb™ on August 15, 2021 tagging @basharjkatou. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'bjh I decided to share my knowledge to help save others like me time and money when starting their Amazon business. I have the time now Check it out! Follow @basharjkatou'.
